Package: dbtr
Title: Diabetes Technologies Research Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonathan", "Williman", , "jonathan.williman@otago.ac.nz", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5080-4435"))
Description: A collection of R tools for working with data generated by diabetes technologies including CGM sensors and pumps. Primarily developed for research rather than individual use. Simplifies API process for extracting data from Nightscout and creating summary metrics.
